These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
City: edinburgh, rome, paris, miami
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
4. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
7. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person traveling to rome and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person traveling to paris and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | edinburgh | rome | paris     | miami |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, oliveros, havana
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the havana-smoker and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the game-smoker is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
4. the old-henry-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | old-henry | game | oliveros      | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
City: hamburg, rome, new-york, marseilles
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person traveling to rome and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | rome    | new-york   | hamburg    | marseilles  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, chinchilla, snake
1. the owner of the bird is the dressmaker##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the owner of the snake have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | chinchilla             | horse          | snake | bird    |

