4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | mystery | horror | adventure | drama |
| Pet   | goat         | pony | ferret    | chinchilla   |

