.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, singing, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: spinach, onion, apple, orange
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating onion##7
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person eating orange##8
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating apple##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person eating spinach##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating orange have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | onion     | apple     | orange     | spinach    |

