.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, musical, spy, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
2. the person watching western movies and the person driving the trike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the trike##7
6. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | spy | sports   | musical | western |
| Transport   | tram   | snowmobile | car    | trike      |

