.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-11::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, cat, ferret, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, puzzles, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | rabbit | fish | cat   | ferret   |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | puzzles   | magic-tricks | gardening |

