.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, strawberry, pomegranate, eggplant
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, trike
1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
3. the person eating eggplant and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the trike is the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | strawberry  | eggplant  | pomegranate | asparagus    |
| Transport     | taxi | trike | bike  | helicopter |

