The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, disco, hip-hop, salsa
1. the person who's birthday is in september and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan salsa is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the fan d&b and the fan salsa##7
4. the fan salsa is somewhere between the fan hip-hop and the person who's birthday is in march##7
5. the fan disco is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | december | march | september | july  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | disco | salsa | hip-hop |

