4. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the tower house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
8. the gothic-revival house and the person drinking almond-milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the modern house and the person drinking sprite have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
