.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, security-guard, writer
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, orange, grey
1. the writer and the person who likes blood-red have the same parity positions##9
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
4. the writer is not to the right of the freelancer##8
5. the person who likes blood-red is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes orange and the electrician have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who likes blood-red and the security-guard have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | electrician | writer | freelancer | security-guard |
| Pet   | orange    | white   | grey        | blood-red            |

