The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, epic, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk and the person watching zombie movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | epic | zombie   | horror   | fantasy   |

