.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, juice, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, entrepreneur, architect, journalist
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the videographer##1
 2. the architect is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 3. the journalist is not to the right of the architect##8
 4. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
 5. the videographer is not the person drinking cola##6
 6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking water and the entrepreneur have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 9. the person drinking water is the entrepreneur##1
10. the person drinking cola and the entrepreneur have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | journalist | architect | entrepreneur | videographer |

 